Revision of Object and class concept. SHORT

Here’s a very short revision (easy to memorize) 👇

🔹 Object
Object = Instance of a class (real-world entity)

It contains data + functions

Example:
Car c1; → c1 is object

🔹 Class
Class = Blueprint/template to create objects

Defines variables + methods

Example:

class Car {
public:
    int speed;
};
🔹 Key Point
Class = Design




